<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>USSR Banner</title>

<style>

body{
    margin:0;
    background:#7a0000;
    overflow:hidden;
    font-family:Arial,sans-serif;
}

.container{
    text-align:center;
    margin-top:40px;
}

.title{
    color:gold;
    font-size:48px;
    font-weight:bold;
}

.subtitle{
    color:gold;
    font-size:22px;
    margin-top:15px;
}

.flags{
    position:absolute;
    bottom:20px;
    font-size:70px;
    white-space:nowrap;
    animation:move 25s linear infinite;
}

@keyframes move{
    from{
        transform:translateX(-100%);
    }
    to{
        transform:translateX(100vw);
    }
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

<div class="title">
☭ USSR LEGACY ☭
</div>

<div class="subtitle">
🇷🇺 🇺🇦 🇧🇾 🇲🇩 🇪🇪 🇱🇻 🇱🇹 🇬🇪 🇦🇲 🇦🇿 🇰🇿 🇰🇬 🇹🇯 🇹🇲 🇺🇿
</div>

</div>

<div class="flags">
🇷🇺 🇺🇦 🇧🇾 🇲🇩 🇪🇪 🇱🇻 🇱🇹 🇬🇪 🇦🇲 🇦🇿 🇰🇿 🇰🇬 🇹🇯 🇹🇲 🇺🇿
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
🇷🇺 🇺🇦 🇧🇾 🇲🇩 🇪🇪 🇱🇻 🇱🇹 🇬🇪 🇦🇲 🇦🇿 🇰🇿 🇰🇬 🇹🇯 🇹🇲 🇺🇿
</div>

</body>
</html>
